{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dive into this unique single-player adventure that contains plenty of unique characters, but zero &quot;NPCs&quot;. (Non-Playable Characters)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is because you \u2013 a sentient, cursed sword known as a <strong>Soulblade</strong>, have the ability to take control of anyone who grips your hilt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2783100/extras/attempt_4.gif?t=1728576940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this Germanic Folklore-inspired HD2D RPG (with rogue-lite &amp; metroidvania elements), your Soulblade abilities will allow you to take control and interact as every character in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Control different characters and change faction loyalties from within.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Rebuild the abandoned Sword Keep and use it as your base of operations. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Recruit characters from different factions with different roles to join you at your Keep.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Forge yourself using skilled recruits &amp; powerful resources to increase your Soulblade powers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Challenge difficult foes and learn more about the Swordbearers who came before you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2783100/extras/616x616-Posession.gif?t=1728576940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a Soulblade, you're not just juggling your own stats and abilities \u2013 you're also pulling the strings on the lives of the bodies you possess. Your choices will shape the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2783100/extras/616x616-Posession-2.gif?t=1728576940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While all characters are playable, and all characters are recruitable after you begin rebuilding your keep, you will still need to make your choices wisely. Roles like the Blacksmith will have effects on the quality of upgrades you can perform based on the faction the recruited NPC originates from.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So, are you ready to unleash your inner blade and let the adventure begin?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2783100/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728576940","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2783100/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1728576940","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2783100/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728576940","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2783100/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728576940","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,5],"notes":"Contains fantasy violence"},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dive into this unique single-player adventure that contains plenty of unique characters, but zero &quot;NPCs&quot;. (Non-Playable Characters)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is because you \u2013 a sentient, cursed sword known as a <strong>Soulblade</strong>, have the ability to take control of anyone who grips your hilt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2783100/extras/attempt_4.gif?t=1728576940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this Germanic Folklore-inspired HD2D RPG (with rogue-lite &amp; metroidvania elements), your Soulblade abilities will allow you to take control and interact as every character in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Control different characters and change faction loyalties from within.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Rebuild the abandoned Sword Keep and use it as your base of operations. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Recruit characters from different factions with different roles to join you at your Keep.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Forge yourself using skilled recruits &amp; powerful resources to increase your Soulblade powers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Challenge difficult foes and learn more about the Swordbearers who came before you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2783100/extras/616x616-Posession.gif?t=1728576940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a Soulblade, you're not just juggling your own stats and abilities \u2013 you're also pulling the strings on the lives of the bodies you possess. Your choices will shape the world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2783100/extras/616x616-Posession-2.gif?t=1728576940\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While all characters are playable, and all characters are recruitable after you begin rebuilding your keep, you will still need to make your choices wisely. Roles like the Blacksmith will have effects on the quality of upgrades you can perform based on the faction the recruited NPC originates from.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So, are you ready to unleash your inner blade and let the adventure begin?</p>","developers":["Baladidog Games"],"genres":[{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2783100/header.jpg?t=1728576940","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257011657,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257011657/movie480.mp4?t=1713912791","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257011657/movie_max.mp4?t=1713912791"},"name":"Blade's Burden - Gameplay","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257011657/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1713912791","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257011657/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1713912791","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257011657/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1713912791"}}],"name":"Blade's Burden","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br></li><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10 / 11 64-bit<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> AMD Ryzen\u2122 3 1200 / Intel\u00ae Core\u2122 i3-6100<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> AMD Radeon\u2122 RX 460 / NVIDIA\u00ae GeForce\u00ae GTX 750<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> Version 12<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 5 GB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li